[30;1m2 | [0m[35m"""Identify a column of text that contains hierarchical id and treeify that column.[0m

[30;1m3965 | [0m[35m    cross-checks the purchase price of a lot against all the other legs that are[0m

[30;1m3970 | [0m[35m    somehow reported an incorrect price you will get an error).[0m

[30;1m2967 | [0m[35m    is present and more recent than the file itself, or update the contents of[0m
[30;1m2968 | [0m[35m    the cache after loading if not. (This works a bit like .pyc byte-compilation[0m

[30;1m2830 | [0m[35m    on the percision of timestamps from the filesystem. Filesystems implement[0m
